aboutBlock.title: What you need to know, before you ask.

featuredSessions.description: We’re super excited to announce GDG DevFest 2019 - San Francisco! A community-run, one-day conference aimed to bring ~300 students, developers, tech-companies and awesome speakers together under one roof where they can learn about Google’s technologies along with other emerging technologies with topics such as Android, Flutter, Firebase, Google Cloud Platform, Mobile, Web, Google Assistant, Machine Learning and more.
